# --- Secrets.xcconfig (Google AI / local xcconfig) ---
# Do NOT commit API keys. Copy LearnHappyGerman/Secrets.xcconfig.example →
# LearnHappyGerman/Secrets.xcconfig and set GOOGLE_AI_API_KEY. Build injects the key into
# Info.plist via AppSecrets.xcconfig → INFOPLIST_KEY_GOOGLE_AI_API_KEY → $(GOOGLE_AI_API_KEY).
# Swift reads the key only from Info.plist (see GoogleGenerativeAIConfiguration).
LearnHappyGerman/Secrets.xcconfig
